  "graph_001_description": "<p>Jumla ya nishati ya kimataifa kutoka kwa kila chanzo kinachohitajika kukidhi mahitaji ya nishati ya kimataifa.</p><p>Nishati ya msingi ni jumla ya nishati kutoka kwa chanzo cha nishati ghafi ambayo inabadilishwa kuwa nishati inayoweza kutumika. Kwa mfano, mahitaji ya msingi ya nishati ya mafuta hurejelea jumla ya kiasi cha nishati ya mafuta yasiyosafishwa ambayo hutolewa, kusafishwa na kutumiwa. Nishati ya msingi ni kubwa kuliko matumizi ya mwisho ya nishati kwa sababu inachangia uzembe katika usindikaji wa mafuta, ubadilishaji wa mafuta na usambazaji na usambazaji (T&amp;D).</p><p>Jumla ya mahitaji ya msingi ya nishati iko katika exajoules kwa mwaka (10<sup>18</sup> joules/mwaka) kwa kila chanzo cha nishati kwa vyanzo vya umeme na visivyo vya umeme kwa pamoja. \"Renewables\" hujumlisha upepo, jua, nishati ya maji na jotoardhi.</p><p class=\"calibration-header\">Urekebishaji:&nbsp;</p><ul>\n<li>Primary demand of energy sources history is calibrated to <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.iea.org/data-and-statistics/data-product/world-energy-balances\">IEA World Energy Balances Datasets, 1990-2023 (2025)</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.energyinst.org/statistical-review\">EI Statistical Review of World Energy (2025)</a>. Projections are compared against <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.iea.org/reports/world-energy-outlook-2025\">IEA World Energy Outlook (2025)</a>, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.ngfs.net/ngfs-scenarios-portal/\">NGFS (version 4.2, 2024)</a>, and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tntcat.iiasa.ac.at/SspDb/dsd?Action=htmlpage&amp;page=10\">SSP Database Version 2.0 (2018)</a>.</li>\n</ul>",
  "graph_001_mini_title": "Kiwango cha awali cha Uhitaji Nishati",
  "graph_001_title": "Vyanzo vya awali vya Nishati Duniani",
  "graph_002_description": "<p>Jumla ya nishati ya kimataifa kutoka kwa kila chanzo kinachohitajika kukidhi mahitaji ya nishati ya kimataifa.</p><p>Nishati ya msingi inarejelea jumla ya nishati kutoka kwa chanzo cha nishati ghafi ambayo inabadilishwa kuwa nishati inayoweza kutumika. Kwa mfano, mahitaji ya msingi ya nishati ya mafuta hurejelea jumla ya kiasi cha nishati ya mafuta yasiyosafishwa ambayo hutolewa, kusafishwa na kutumiwa. Nishati ya msingi ni kubwa kuliko matumizi ya mwisho ya nishati kwa sababu inachangia uzembe katika usindikaji wa mafuta, ubadilishaji wa mafuta na usambazaji na usambazaji (T&amp;D).</p><p>Jumla ya mahitaji ya msingi ya nishati iko katika exajoules kwa mwaka (10<sup>18</sup> joules/mwaka) kwa kila chanzo cha nishati kwa vyanzo vya umeme na visivyo vya umeme kwa pamoja. \"Renewables\" hujumlisha upepo, jua, nishati ya maji na jotoardhi.</p><p class=\"calibration-header\">Urekebishaji:&nbsp;</p><ul>\n<li>Primary demand of energy sources history is calibrated to <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.iea.org/data-and-statistics/data-product/world-energy-balances\">IEA World Energy Balances Datasets, 1990-2023 (2025)</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.energyinst.org/statistical-review\">EI Statistical Review of World Energy (2025)</a>. Projections are compared against <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.iea.org/reports/world-energy-outlook-2025\">IEA World Energy Outlook (2025)</a>, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.ngfs.net/ngfs-scenarios-portal/\">NGFS (version 4.2, 2024)</a>, and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tntcat.iiasa.ac.at/SspDb/dsd?Action=htmlpage&amp;page=10\">SSP Database Version 2.0 (2018)</a>.</li>\n</ul>",
