  "graph_003_description": "<p>Mahitaji ya msingi ya nishati ya makaa ya mawe katika exajoules kwa mwaka (joule 10<sup>18</sup> mwaka) kwa vyanzo vya umeme na visivyo vya umeme kwa pamoja.</p><p>Nishati ya msingi ni jumla ya nishati kutoka kwa chanzo cha nishati ghafi ambayo inabadilishwa kuwa nishati inayoweza kutumika. Kwa mfano, mahitaji ya msingi ya nishati ya makaa ya mawe hurejelea jumla ya nishati katika makaa ambayo huchimbwa, kusindika na kuliwa. Nishati ya msingi ni kubwa kuliko matumizi ya mwisho ya nishati kwa sababu inachangia uzembe katika usindikaji wa mafuta, ubadilishaji wa mafuta na usambazaji na usambazaji (T&amp;D).</p><p class=\"calibration-header\">Urekebishaji:&nbsp;</p><ul>\n<li>Primary demand of energy sources history is calibrated to <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.iea.org/data-and-statistics/data-product/world-energy-balances\">IEA World Energy Balances Datasets, 1990-2023 (2025)</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.energyinst.org/statistical-review\">EI Statistical Review of World Energy (2025)</a>. Projections are compared against <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.iea.org/reports/world-energy-outlook-2025\">IEA World Energy Outlook (2025)</a>, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.ngfs.net/ngfs-scenarios-portal/\">NGFS (version 4.2, 2024)</a>, and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tntcat.iiasa.ac.at/SspDb/dsd?Action=htmlpage&amp;page=10\">SSP Database Version 2.0 (2018)</a>.</li>\n</ul>",
