  "input_171_description": "<p>Kiasi gani cha gharama huanguka kutokana na kujifunza, uzoefu na uchumi wa kiwango. Thamani ya chini inaonyesha ujifunzaji wa haraka. Kwa kila kuongezeka maradufu kwa uwezo uliosakinishwa, gharama huzidishwa kwa uwiano wa maendeleo. Kwa mfano, ikiwa uwiano wa maendeleo ni 0.8, basi gharama itapungua kwa 20% kadri uzoefu unavyoongezeka maradufu. Dhana hii inatumika kwa ujenzi wa baadaye. Thamani za zamani zinasawazishwa kwa gharama na uwezo unaojulikana.</p><p class=\"sources-header\">Vyanzo:&nbsp;</p><ul>\n<li>Junginger, M., van Sark, W., &amp; Faaij, A. (2010). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.4337/9781849806848\"><i>Technological learning in the energy sector: Lessons for policy, industry and science.</i></a> Edward Elgar.</li>\n<li>McDonald, A., &amp; Schrattenholzer, L. (2001). <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1016/s0301-4215(00)00122-1\">Learning rates for Energy Technologies.</a> <i>Energy Policy, 29</i>(4), 255–261.</li>\n</ul>",
